Package: phaserR
Title: An R Interface to the Phaser.js Game Framework
Version: 0.0.0.9005
Authors@R: 
    person("Maciej", "Banas", , "banasmaciek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package provides an R-based API to build and control 2D games using the Phaser.js JavaScript engine. It enables integration with Shiny applications, allowing R developers to create interactive games and simulations using a declarative R syntax.
